
class Solution {
public:
    int minSteps(int n) {
        int steps = 0;
        for(int i=2 ; i<=n ; i++){
            while(n%i == 0){
                steps += i;
                n /= i;
            }
        }
        return steps;
    }
};


TC: O(√n)
Space Complexity: O(1)
Although the loop runs till n, the number gets reduced quickly due to division, so the effective complexity is O(√n)

